The Hamburger Stand set contains a hamburger shop in the shape of a hamburger, plus a delivery bike and much much more!

The Hamburger Stand is the newest food spot in Sylvania!

The owner of the hamburger stand is Matteo the Latte Cat father, he is wearing a special hamburger shop uniform that is only available with this set. Matteo’s hamburgers are very popular and villagers line up to buy them in places like the amusement park and village square.

entry.title: Sylvanian Families Seal Family - A new family in Sylvania
entry.summary:
Vendor: Sylvanian Families
Type: Sylvanian Families
Price: 34.90

Sylvanian Families Seal Family - Released mid 2024 - SF 5759

Introducing the Floater Seal Family, Father Maurice, Mother Amora and Puffy and Muffy. Being seals, they love nothing more than to swim. They'll fit right in, whether they're in Far North Queensland or Tasmania!

Father Maurice Floater - is a speedy swimmer, he used to be known as the Sea Breeze Cape speedster, although now a days he is more than often found lazing around and having his belly poked by the babies. 

Mother Amora Floater - is a laid-back mum. She is always out shopping for lot of fun toys for her babies, and is often heard saying “Freeze it for now!” She believes that time stops when she freezes things, so her freezer is always full!

Baby Boy Puffy Floater - is a cautious type. He can’t let go of his floatie when he's in the water, which makes him a little frustrated because his sister Moffy is a good swimmer. He is practicing swimming with his Father, so that one day he can do it on his own!

Baby Girl Moffy Floater - is an active baby who can swim with ease, unlike her brother. She jumps into the water without fear and surprises everyone around her.

The Seal Family have cute, round features. They have distinctive eyebrow-like markings, dimpled ears, and whiskers around their mouths. This set contains the father, mother and babies, along with pool accessories.

This set includes: Seal Father, Seal Mother, Seal Baby, Seal Baby (crawling), vinyl bag, swimming ring, beach ball

Recommended for age 3+


SF 5759
